-- Russia Sees No Alternative to Kofi Annan’s Syria Peace Plan
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-06-03T13:13:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-03/russia-sees-no-alternative-to-kofi-annan-s-syria-peace-plan.html
Kofi Annan’s Syria peace plan doesn’t
have an alternative, Russia’s Foreign Affairs Minister  Sergei Lavrov  said during a phone conversation with Annan today,
according to a statement on the ministry’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
